stateDiagram-v2
  [*] --> Proposed: 父 Agent 提出 DelegateIntent
  Proposed --> Validated: 结构与范围通过
  Validated --> Rejected: 越界/缺少能力
  Validated --> Running: 权限允许
  Running --> NeedsApproval: 子 Agent 请求高风险动作
  NeedsApproval --> Running: 父 Agent/用户批准
  NeedsApproval --> Constrained: 拒绝并收窄范围
  Constrained --> Running: 继续只做安全子集
  Running --> Completed: 返回结构化结果
  Running --> Failed: 超时/取消/工具失败
  Failed --> Recovered: 父 Agent 回收或重派
  Completed --> Joined: 父 Agent review & join
  Recovered --> Joined
  Rejected --> Joined
  Joined --> [*]
